				</div>
                				<h4><a href="//dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/11/04/invesco-fund-treads-risky-path-as-major-investor-in-distressed-debt/?ref=dealbook">Invesco Fund Treads Risky Path as Major Investor in Distressed Corporate Debt</a></h4>
				<p class="nyt-article-byline">By LANDON THOMAS JR.</p>
				<p class="nyt-article-summary">Investors seeking high yields have poured billions into Invescoâs PowerShares suite of exchange-traded funds, but regulators worry that a lack of liquidity could hamper redemptions if the market softens.</p>
			</div>
			
